## 1.4 Hardware Tech (9 businesses)

---

### 🟡 31. IoT Devices & Smart Home

**What it is:** Building internet-connected devices — smart switches, sensors, home automation, GPS trackers, health monitors.

**Players:** Xiaomi Smart Home (big), Amazon Echo (big), Oakter (Indian, small), SenseGiz (Indian, small).

**Model:** Product Sale 📦 + Subscription 🔄 (cloud) | **Revenue:** 🔄 Medium — 6-12 months to first product.

**Challenges:** 🧠 Hardware + firmware + software + cloud — multidisciplinary · 💰 Manufacturing MOQs · ⚙ Hardware bugs can't be patched · 📜 BIS certification mandatory · 🌊 Component supply issues.

**Mistake:** Starting with consumer products. B2B IoT (factory monitoring, cold chain tracking) pays more and forgives more.

**One-liner:** Build smart connected devices — start B2B before attempting consumer products.

---

### 🔴 32. Drones & Robotics

**What it is:** Designing drones/robots for agriculture (crop spraying), surveying, filming, warehouses, defense.

**Players:** DJI (big, Chinese), ideaForge (Indian, big), Garuda Aerospace (Indian), GreyOrange (Indian, warehouse robots).

